    "description": {
      "es": "",
      "en": "Write a representation of the configuration to the specified file object, which must be opened in text mode (accepting strings). This representation can be parsed by a future read() call. If space_around_delimiters is true, delimiters between keys and values are surrounded by spaces. Changed in version 3.14: Raises InvalidWriteError if this would write a representation which cannot be accurately parsed by a future read() call from this parser."
